title: Ep 65: The Judgies got work done
description:
In this Episode: A woman forgot to mention her plastic surgery to her new BF and drama ensues, a man begins to refuse to drive his GF to her dance classes, a fitness enthusist gets told she needs to wear a bra if she is going to the gym, and a listener feels bad for not complaining about her terrible coworker. We also go over some internet ideas Josh thought of now that we have become so successful.
